sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant FE as RatingForm (Next.js)
  participant BE as FastAPI Backend
  participant TL as TLSTMFuzzy Predictor
  participant GX as Gemini Explainer
  participant GM as Gemini API
  participant ST as MODEL_STATE
  participant HC as prediction_history.csv

  U->>FE: Upload CSV + chọn dòng
  FE->>FE: Parse CSV theo header\nmap 12 financial fields
  U->>FE: Submit phân tích

  FE->>BE: POST /api/predict\n(features)
  BE->>TL: predict_tlstm(...)
  TL-->>BE: rating + probabilities + confidence + risk_score
  BE-->>FE: PredictResult

  FE->>FE: buildXaiContext()\nbuildTlstmExplainInput()

  FE->>BE: POST /api/history\n(prediction + features + ticker/company)
  BE->>ST: append in-memory data_df
  BE->>HC: append CSV history
  BE-->>FE: saved=true

  FE->>BE: POST /api/explain\n(features + prediction + tlstm_prediction + xai_context)
  BE->>GX: generate_gemini_explanation(...)
  GX->>GM: chat.completions.create(...)
  GM-->>GX: explanation text
  GX-->>BE: explanation
  BE-->>FE: provider/model/explanation

  FE-->>U: Hiển thị rating, risk, probabilities,\nRisk Interpretation (Gemini)
